title: How I Fixed My Life
subtitle: Chapter 5: Super Jiana
preview: In the simplest of terms, I don’t know what I’m doing in life. I don’t know what it is I’m put on this Earth to do in the best, most unique, Jiana way that I can. I keep reading and every resource tells me that I will find that given the right tools, mindset, and persistence, but it’s hard to tell someone they’ll find their life raft in the middle of the ocean while they’re drowning.
